1. Introduction

Kiddotubes (“we”, “us”) runs the Kiddotubes service for children and parents. This Privacy Policy describes what digital personal data we collect, why we collect it, how we use and share it, your rights, and how to contact us. We process personal data in accordance with India’s Digital Personal Data Protection (DPDP) Act and Rules. 
