2. Scope & Applicability

Applies to personal data collected in India through our website, apps, or services, including data collected offline and digitised for offering services to users in India. 
PRS Legislative Research

3. Types of Data We Collect

Account & profile data: name, parent email, username, hashed password.
Child profile data: child display name, age bracket (required for age-appropriate content). We do NOT require persistent precise identifiers for children (e.g., full legal name) unless necessary.
Usage & device data: IP, device identifiers, app telemetry, videos watched, watch-time, preferences.
Support & communications: email messages, support logs.
Payment data: (if applicable) tokenized/third-party payment provider data only.
Optional: profile photos only if parent explicitly uploads them.

4. Lawful Basis & Purpose

We collect and use personal data for: account setup, content personalization, analytics & quality improvement, parental communications, safety moderation, payments, legal compliance, and security. For children’s data we rely on verifiable parental consent where required. (DPDP rules require verifiable parental consent for processing children’s data and limit collection to what is necessary). 
