We collect only minimal necessary data for service operation and age-appropriate content.

We will not sell or transfer children’s personal data for advertising or marketing without parental opt-in.

6. Data Retention

We retain personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes described, or as required by law. Example retention periods (edit as appropriate): account & profile data — until account deletion + 2 years; support logs — 12 months; anonymized analytics — 36 months.

7. Data Sharing & Transfers

We do not sell personal data. We may share limited data with: service providers (hosting, analytics, payment processors), legal authorities (to comply with law), and in a merger/acquisition event (with notice). Cross-border transfers will comply with DPDP safeguards and any applicable contractual protections. 
